intro to schema design:
  - to embed or not to embed, that is the question
  - document oriented scheme (straightforward with relational)
    - posts collection had a tags array embedded (which could be duplicated between posts)
    - accessed at the same time you access the post, not independently.
  - when deciding to embed, the way you access the data that decides
  - a mongodb document cant be larger than 16MB

